verbose_text: Notably, the A/J hypomorphic Naip5 allele that is associated with permissiveness to Legionella replication, does not fully impair the caspase-1 pathway, whereas macrophages from Naip5 -/- mice that are similarly permissive to bacterial replication, exhibit significantly blunted caspase-1 activation.
evidence: A/J hypomorphic Naip5 allele that is associated with permissiveness to Legionella replication, does not fully impair the caspase-1
